						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of the Gaṇēśa temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1530 (expired) <hi rend="bold">Plavaṅga, Mārgaśira, śu. 13,</hi> corresponding to 1607 A.D., November 21, Saturday.</p>						

						<p>It records the grant of grain income (called <hi rend="italic">Kuṇṭa-Tūmulu</hi>) made by <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Rāmarāju Mūṛti Krishnamarājayyadēva Mahārāju for the maintenance of the tanks at Perimiḍi.</p>						

						</summary>
