<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī jayābhyudaya śālivāhana 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śakavarṣaṁbulu 1530 Agunē<unclear>ṁ</unclear>ṭi 
<lb n="3"/>plavaṁga saṁvatsara mārgaśira śu 13 lu śrīmaṁnma 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>hāmaṁḍalēśvara rājādhirāja rājaparamēśvara rāmarāju 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>mūrti <unclear>kriṣṇa</unclear>ma rājayyadēva mahārājayyagāru śēśina 
<lb n="6"/>dharmaśāsanaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> peśimiḍi ceruvulaku guṁṭa tūmulu ceru 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>vulamīda vēśē Aṁduku Icina dharma śāsanaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yī dhānyaṁ 
<lb n="8"/>yavaru Apahariṁceḍivāru vāru kartta gōbrā 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṁhmaṁnnivadhiyiṁccina pāpāna pōduru mātā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> vadha cēśina dōṣāna pōduru <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/>bāla <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vāsaṁ Aṁdu jiṁtiṁcu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vāni kaḍupuna puṭuduru 
</p>

